<lb n="1"/>śrīmatsūrapanāyakaḥ kulanidhirggōpānvaya<unclear>ssu</unclear>
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ndarastasmāduttananāya<unclear>kasta</unclear>dabalā callāṁbikāsundarī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="3"/>tābhyāṁ dēvāhvayōbhūdakhilaguṇanidhirbbhīmanādhāya
<lb n="4"/>dīpaṁ dākṣārāmēśvarāya tribhuvanatilakāyādarā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>llōkabharttre [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 1*] dharitrībhēśaśākābdē caitraśuklārkkavāsa
