<lb n="7"/>śakavaruṣaṁbulu 1181 gu nēṁṇṭi caitra(śu)
<lb n="8"/>śuddha 1 miyu ravivāramunāṁḍu UttanabōIni kō
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ḍku dēvanabōyuṁḍu tamaku dhammārtthamugānu śrībhī
<lb n="10" break="no"/>manāthadēvarakuṁ beṭṭina Akhaṁḍḍavartti lōhadiviya
<lb n="11" break="no"/>daṁḍu Okkaṁṭṭiki ḍaṁppakāmaṭṭi EṟiyabōIni vaśa
<lb n="12" break="no"/>munaṁ be(ṁ)ṭṭina mōdālu 50 bōlu naluvura pūṁṭṭagānu
<lb n="13"/>tribhuvanāṁkkuśamāna nitya māneṁḍu neI naḍapaṁggalā
<lb n="14" break="no"/>ṁḍu Ācaṁdrārkkamugānu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>
